USA: EU kanske slipper biltullar
USA kanske inte behöver införa tullar på import av bilar från EU. Det säger USA:s handelsminister Wilbur Ross. Han säger sig ha haft ”goda samtal med billtillverkare” i bland annat EU och Japan, rapporterar  Bloomberg News.
03 Nov 2019, 14:51 by TT

text:
USA: The EU may not allow car tariffs
The US may not have to impose tariffs on imports of cars from the EU. So says US Secretary of Commerce Wilbur Ross. He says he has had "good talks with car manufacturers" in the EU and Japan, for example, reports Bloomberg News.
03 Nov 2019, 14:51 by TT
